trending_videos.title: Draft Day
trending_videos.description: Sonny Weaver Jr. is the general manager of the Cleveland Browns. One of pro football's most important days, NFL draft day, is drawing near, but Sonny has much more on his mind than just which players to recruit. His lover is pregnant, and the team's owner wants to fire him. After Sonny accepts a deal with Seattle that nets him that team's first-round pick, he immediately wonders if he has made the right choice for himself and the Browns.

trending_videos.title: WWE 2K26: Gameplay Trailer Breakdown! New Details, Hidden Features, Showcase Matches & More!
trending_videos.description:
Join us as we breakdown the new WWE 2K26 Gameplay Trailer to reveal of the new content it includes, secrets and hidden features!

The new gameplay trailer features a ton of new footage including the first look at Inferno match gameplay featuring The Undertaker and Kane, Dumpster match gameplay between Michin and Chelsea Green, and new footage of the Scrapyard Brawl area coming to The Island!

Also shown in the trailer were some of the new gameplay features including the return of stackable tables, the new match start feature, barricade brawls, and the new bag of thumbtacks!

The trailer also revealed the addition of a classic version of CM Punk featuring his ROH / TNA gear, with this further adding to the speculation of Steve Corino joining the roster as a new ECW Legend!

What did you think of the trailer? Did you catch anything I missed?
Let me know your thoughts in the comments!
